author: Shaun Walker
description: Rodrigo Duterte embarks on five-day visit as he seeks to loosen ties with Washington and strengthen bond with Russia
title: Philippine president Duterte flies to Moscow to meet 'hero' Putin

author: The Associated Press
description: Philippine President Rodrigo Duterte declared the country's south under martial rule for 60 days.
title: Duterte declares martial rule in south Philippines amid deadly clashes

author: Euan McKirdy and Joshua Berlinger, CNN
description: Philippines President Rodrigo Duterte said his martial law declaration for the country's restive south was necessary in order to fight militants there.
title: Duterte: 'I had to declare martial law' to fight ISIS in Mindanao

author: Felipe Villamor
description: President Rodrigo Duterte stressed that the campaign to defeat Islamic State-linked militants on a southern island would be “harsh.”
title: Duterte Calls on Philippines to Support His Declaration of Martial Law

description: The Latest on the siege of a Philippine city that led President Rodrigo Duterte to declare martial law in the south (all times local):
title: The Latest: Duterte considering nationwide martial law

author: Al Jazeera
description: Ongoing violence prompts 'mass exodus' from Marawi, as President Rodrigo Duterte considers nationwide martial law.
title: Mindanao: Churchgoers 'taken hostage' amid Marawi siege

author: Frances Martel
description: Philippines President Rodrigo Duterte has threatened to expand a 60-day state of emergency in southern Mindanao to the whole country.
title: Duterte Says 'Spare No One' as Islamic State Beheads Police Chief, Stages Mass Prison Break

author: Euan McKirdy, CNN
description: Philippines President Rodrigo Duterte is soon to depart on an official visit Moscow as part of the Asian nation's pivot away from the United States
title: Philippines' Duterte looks to strengthen ties with trip to Moscow

author: Anna Christin Koch
description: Seit Monaten führt Präsident Rodrigo Duterte einen erbitterten Kampf gegen Drogen. Jetzt will er auch das Rauchen verbieten.
title: Rauchen kann dich auf den Philippinen bald ins Gefängnis bringen

author: Andreo Calonzo, Siegfrid Alegado
description: Philippine President Rodrigo Duterte placed the southern island of Mindanao under military rule Tuesday night after terrorists linked to Islamic State clashed with government troops in Marawi, the most populous city in the island’s Muslim region.
title: Duterte Puts Mindanao Under Martial Law After Terrorist Clashes
